2.caption: 1934 Major League Baseball All-Star Game
2.description: Cy Pfirman, NL (home), Brick Owens, AL (first base), Dolly Stark, NL (second base), George Moriarty, AL (third base); the umpires rotated positions clockwise in the middle of the fifth inning, with Owens moving behind the plate.
2.inspected:Radio announcers: France Laux, Ted Husing (CBS)Tom Manning, Ford Bond, Graham McNamee (NBC)
